(1) package.json File Included In The Project And Has 2 Benefits
----------------------------------------------------------------
==> Let's You Manage The Dependencies Of The Project
==> Helps To Add Script That Help With Intial Build Of Project

(2) Create [package.json] File
-------------------------------
==> npm init
==> Hit Enter For Every Thing 

(3) Create [package.json] Without Asking Questions
---------------------------------------------------
==> [npm init --yes] Or [npm init -y]

